cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "Human-AI Interaction Layer Reviewer"
abstract: >-
  An open-source tool that audits the human-AI interaction layer of an AI
  system (how it presents results, whether it can be corrected, and whether its
  alerts fire at the right time) against Microsoft's HAX-18 and Google's PAIR
  design guidelines, producing evidence-anchored findings mapped to the EU AI
  Act and the NIST AI RMF.
type: software
